snippet: Novak Djokovic defeated Alejandro González, 6-1, 3-6, 6-1, ending González’s surprising run to the third round at the BNP Paribas Open in Indian Wells, Calif.
abstract: Novak Djokovic beats Alejandro Gonzalez in the third round at the BNP Paribas Open; other tennis news noted.
